    {\displaystyle [\![x_{1}]\!]\in [\![{\mathsf {T}}_{1}]\!],~[\![x_{2}]\!]\in [\![{\mathsf {T}}_{2}]\!],~\ldots ,~[\![x_{n}]\!]\in [\![{\mathsf {T}}_{n}]\!]}
  .The n-tuple of type theory has the natural interpretation as an n-tuple of set theory:

  
    
      
